replies.body:
{{item:3102}} 

Punishes mages for casting spells. Still available.

{{item:2051}} 

Spells lower the CD

etc. Including some champ skills.

I'm not asking for an item that will 100% invalidate AD spells, I'm just asking for something I can build that would make the enemy at least thing twice about using the spell on me. or, at the very least, give me a little better defense than a purely statistical boost.
